            "evidence": "SPEC.md:1567-1576 \u00c2\u00a724 starter content; SPEC.md:1513 \u00c2\u00a722 step 27; SPEC.md:1766 DoD #1; SPEC.md:1442-1446 \u00c2\u00a721.1 golden-file conformance suite."
