          "payload": {
            "reason": "task 001 produced mojibake output (Claude Read tool decoded UTF-8 project files as cp1252 on Windows). Project files now BOM'd and LF-normalized to force UTF-8 decoding. Daemon also patched to v2.2.1 (atomic_write retries on transient PermissionError, primary cause of task 002's missing audit entry).",
            "reset_fields": {
