          "The SPEC \u00c2\u00a713.5 describes instance-on-instance merge as a user option on collision; the IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN \u00c2\u00a71.7 scopes the function to abort-and-report only. Is the merge path out of scope for task 1.7 entirely, or should it be a follow-up chain?",
