                "file": "project/SPEC.md",
                "lines": "902",
                "excerpt": "The v0.2 \u00e2\u2020\u2019 v0.3 portion of the migration (adding `ecm:specVersion`, initializing `ecm:literalAssertions`, etc.) is applied first; the v0.3 \u00e2\u2020\u2019 v0.4 portion runs on top of the result."
              }
